# get_irida_sample_assemblies_metadata
# get assembly metadata for a sample. Does not download any files.
# PROJECT_ID is used only for tab completion, not passed to the API
# SAMPLE_ID is the actual argument used in the curl call
#
# example: get_irida_sample_assemblies_metadata [TAB once for project id] 105:Slush_Sub [TAB again for sample id] 7709:Strain0016
